.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: crime, spy, thriller, satire, romance
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: lily, aconite, azalea, iris, orchid
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-gold, kools, chesterfields, lucky-strike, parliaments
City: berlin, london, boston, paris, miami
5 different pets are kept: dog, fox, zebra, horse, snails

1. the person who growslily is the person watching crime movies
2. the person who growsaconite is the owner of the dog
3. the person traveling to berlin is the person watching spy movies
4. the person who growsazalea is the person traveling to london
5. the person watching spy movies is to the right of the person watching thriller movies
6. the old-gold-smoker is the owner of the snails
7. the kools-smoker is the person watching satire movies
8. the person traveling to boston is in the middle
9. the person who growsiris is on the far left
10. the chesterfields-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the fox
11. the kools-smoker is to the left or right of the owner of the horse
12. the lucky-strike-smoker is the person traveling to paris
13. the person who growsorchid is the parliaments-smoker
14. the person who growsiris is to the left or right of the person watching romance movies

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Flower	|   iris	|    azalea	|     lily	|    aconite	|    orchid	|
| Movie-Genre		|    satire	|      romance	|      crime	|     thriller	|     spy	|
| City	|     miami	|      london	|      boston	| paris	|     berlin	|
| Cigar		|     kools	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| lucky-strike	|   parliament	|
| Pet		|     fox	|     horse	|     snails	|     dog	|     zebra	|
